### 유저 생성
POST http://localhost:19093/api/v1/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json
#X-User-Name: tester
#X-User-Role: CUSTOMER
#X-User-ID: 3

{
  "username": "tester",
  "password": "12345678a*",
  "nickname": "테스터",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "contact": "010-1111-2222"
}

### 유저 조회(개인)
GET http://localhost:19093/api/v1/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Name: tester
X-User-Role: CUSTOMER
X-User-ID: 3

### 유저 정보 수정
PUT http://localhost:19093/api/v1/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Name: tester
X-User-Role: CUSTOMER
X-User-ID: 3

{
  "nickname": "테스터",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "contact": "010-1111-2212"
}
